    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013730/extras/f5ea9fd6e7e69377ef06f6c8d8d9d8f3.avif?t=1771491351\" width=600 height=84 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013730/extras/c92fb509cfb8b1d768fafaabfa164581.poster.avif?t=1771491351\" width=611 height=172 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013730/extras/c92fb509cfb8b1d768fafaabfa164581.webm?t=1771491351\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>第一次离开母亲的家，走出那温暖的巢穴，迎接一个与你一样独特且奢华的世界的秘密吧！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>在这场史诗般的冒险中，你将扮演塞莱斯坦——一位25岁、行为幼稚的“成人孩子”，因一时糊涂犯下过错，不得不踏上征服伊苏地区的旅程。那里满目疮痍，居住着被称为“Risimons”的神秘生物。</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013730/extras/c07dd99bde14ba2fb954729f493dcb6a.poster.avif?t=1771491351\" width=611 height=172 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013730/extras/c07dd99bde14ba2fb954729f493dcb6a.webm?t=1771491351\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013730/extras/350387ad172bb4678450b7e2e722928a.poster.avif?t=1771491351\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013730/extras/350387ad172bb4678450b7e2e722928a.webm?t=1771491351\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013730/extras/350387ad172bb4678450b7e2e722928a.mp4?t=1771491351\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>一旦你离开了温室般的家庭，伊苏地区的秘密全凭你去发掘！ </strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你将扮演塞莱斯坦——一个既不具魅力、也不聪明、也不受人尊敬的“成人孩子”，在一个远远超出你想象的世界中，被迫踏上冒险之旅。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >体验一段既充满讽刺又滑稽荒诞的故事，其辛辣幽默既汲取了当代文化的精髓，也揉入了网络世界的怪诞风格。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从“论坛镇”到“进步港”，再到“恒河峡谷”，各区域各具特色，并拥有无与伦比的居民。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >   </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索众多偏远之地，那里布满独特任务和等待解开的谜团。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >   </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >遇见数百个既疯狂又怪诞的人物和生物，每一个都经过精心编写和绘制。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >跟随查德、艾米莉、科雷坦以及旅途中遇到的所有独特角色的冒险故事！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013730/extras/78513db1ae60af1c42d381c61a064202.poster.avif?t=1771491351\" width=649 height=177 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013730/extras/78513db1ae60af1c42d381c61a064202.webm?t=1771491351\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>你可以捕捉“Risimons”，组建一支战斗队伍，并挑战路上遇到的无数训练师：</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >   </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >寻找并捕捉那些狂野、充满荒诞、讽刺和疯癫主题的生物。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >打造一支足以征服各种试炼、竞技场以及充斥Risimon世界的冠军的团队。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >强化并个性化你的队伍，以迎接游戏中最严峻的挑战！</p></li></ul>",
